Stuff for [http://www.ruby-lang.org/ Object Oriented Scripting Language Ruby].

* RubyMode
* EmacsLispForRuby
* ReLisp (another ruby/emacs bridge)
* LangHelp
* GonzuiForEmacs
* FlymakeRuby
* RubyBlockMode
* RubyTestMode
* [[ruby-debug]] For a more easy way for debugging in ruby.

== Documentation ==
Utilities for consulting the documentation using Ri or other tools.

* RiEl
* [http://www.emacswiki.org/cgi-bin/emacs/YARI YARI] (Yet Another Ri Interface)

== Ruby on Rails ==
Tools specifically used for helping you with developing in [http://rubyonrails.org/ Ruby on Rails].


* RubyOnRails
* [NxhtmlMode nXhtml]


